Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:54.96,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H05F4F5&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord4}如果有人说那是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:23:00.42,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0500FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}和你紧紧相连的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:05.55,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H64CB00&\3c&HFFFFFF&}除了“心灵感应”还能是什么!?
